<dl id="n06054b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06054b">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06054b"> 54(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> HCE Sant Claus</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Pour bien comprendre ce culte, cette superstition de la poup&eacute;e, pour s&apos;expliquer la confiance absolue, l&apos;amour in&eacute;branlable que l&apos;enfant &eacute;prouve &agrave; son &eacute;gard, il serait n&eacute;cessaire de p&eacute;n&eacute;trer la nature de l&apos;illusion &agrave; laquelle elle pr&ecirc;te. L&apos;enfant croit-il &agrave; sa r&eacute;alit&eacute;? <font color="green">[To fully understand this cult, this superstition of the doll, to explain the absolute confidence, the unshakeable love that the child feels towards him, it would be necessary to penetrate the nature of the illusion to which it lends. Does the child believe his reality?]</font> <small> Fr&eacute;d&eacute;ric Queyrat, <a name="FQLJ" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#FQLJ"><cite title="source">Les Jeux des Enfants</cite></a> (1920) 120?</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
